assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Mold-Tek Technologies Limited provides civil, structural, and mechanical engineering services in India, the United States, and internationally. It offers mechanical engineering services in the automotive, poles and towers, and oil and gas domains. The company also provides information technology services. Mold-Tek Technologies Limited was incorporated in 1985 and is headquartered in Hyderabad, India.
